section.def:
driver
                (司機) means, in relation to a motor vehicle, any
            person who is in charge of or assisting in the control of such vehicle;

street
                (街道) includes any gutter, surface channel and
            grass verge adjoining or forming part of any street;

paragraph.content:
in a street or public place, within 6 m of any premises fronting, adjoining
                    or abutting on such street or public place and having direct access thereto;
                        or (L.N. 89 of 1979)
